ta analysis）</li>		<li>基因生物统计遗传相关计算与统计问题（statistical and computational issues arising from the problems in genome biology statistical genetics）</li>		<li>变点检测、参数估计和自适应控制问题在工程、经济和<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/遗传学" target="_blank">遗传学</a>的应用（change-points detection, parameter estimation and adaptive control problems and their applications in engineering, economics and genetics）</li>		<li>统计模型和<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/金融" target="_blank">金融</a><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/计量经济学" target="_blank">计量经济学</a>和工程学方法（statistical models and methods in financial econometrics and engineering）</li>		<li>时间序列建模（time series modeling）</li>		<li>设计和实验、误差变量建模分析、稳健回归分析（design and analysis of experiments, longitudinal and contemporaneous pathway discovery and analysis, errors in variable modeling, robust regression analysis）*(12)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9Lu8kyji76AGfffffiwbVPdwKsXYJvEIEIwkAJIUbgspfwkx4jTk_CfEokFImlcaQVKk7SKj5RhstoW7pNQg1IOrA-a45zot-eQcKREbAhyUsiBOxOTlUqrb3OF0Pdwa3V3VqsAV_adbGC3_vfcm9ncmFtOo0Q8XgM" target="_blank">Applying to the AMS Graduate Program </a>Graduate College of Engineering and Applied Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oGsLWal5sSytjJb_4hj2t9Fr_Ftq57lPWBf-Nz5IkQn-tkCjYYolGhR1PQ8AwZhv4Pxe-PUhU1wr8-UztHpNsm64x-soRSqa74S9zAzUbSMrlnoxfmpCw5QU_" target="_blank">Cost of Attendance</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2tLqEHvPnqDDDDD71uah5maZb26z090mcE01dEq4J9Yzc_yhTHu-QyNAni42bjVItjrIX0x2XuFp0iSl1Bzgecz-8OWJRHp-Gmz5AlG3ntX-Itx34WDwnt1" target="_blank">APPLYING TO THE GRADUATE SCHOOL - FAQs TRANSCRIPTS</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oEvke4w37QheeeeeuwN1ZvQ19tSbHyryQ0gyPOgh37rAH0iDPbqKHzSxIErRHfQxH7QAh1S5Exql1BC5Fpx6JpynqlfRTeyOUpAwP6rnWpgJEuZ" target="_blank">APPLYING TO THE GRADUATE SCHOOL - FAQs TEST SCORES</a> Stony Brook University