ering workforce policy）</li>	<li>智能电网（Smart-grid）</li>	<li>能源环境系统转换（Energy-environmental systems transitions）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/纳米技术" target="_blank">纳米技术</a>研发与推广（Diffusion of nanotechnology R&amp;D）</li>	<li>研发全球化（The globalization of R&amp;D）</li>	<li>环境与废弃物管理（Environmental and waste management）</li>	<li>风险评估（Risk assessment）</li>	<li>国际核安全（International nuclear safety）</li>	<li>气候（Climate）</li>	<li>不平等与贫困所导致的技术影响（Factors and impacts of technology on inequality and poverty）</li>	<li>产业生态（Industrial ecology）</li>	<li>先进技术与新兴技术评估（Technology assessment of advanced and emerging technologies）</li>	<li>科技、数学、工程高等远程师范教育（Advanced technologies in science, technology, engineering and mathematics education Distance learning）</li>	<li>人机接口创新理论（Innovative approaches to human-computer interfaces）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/人力资源管理" target="_blank">人力资源</a>问题，主要是妇女与少数民族（Human resource issues, especially participation of underrepresented minorities and women in science, technology, engineering and mathematics）</li>	<li>美国军控政策，尤其是对大规模杀伤性武器（U.S. arms control policies, particularly dealing with weapons of mass destruction）</li>	<li>核武器、生化反恐（Nuclear, chemical, and biological counter-terrorism）</li>	<li>规划与管理教育技术（Planning and managing educational technologies）*(8)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrkywRjyJFElkkkkkkD8lnkvhL-JefjqjqGo_i8x1pXCeKeXwmWfrEUqeBInlzWs92rLwkryeVvith_1Jil8rts8rxJQ8FnH8DUQSlXO1HYw3f5MpW" target="_blank">Cost of Attendance</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZoCk3FezsUzPPPPPK9shiU3h8nA4ClRl3_Xl9AAMGOJaQ4XWYyu0m4NUqjRa-4Ekq4JkQj1aQKmMj36aYsK0zaPiN6XUV9KT-ES6OU9oR4aF0laYRMSKp4ay" target="_blank">APPLYING TO THE GRADUATE SCHOOL - FAQs TRANSCRIPTS</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=XrChP9_PwYZ8xJ0OcMrFb1ffd5BKhFGhObUa9EO811jgc1qzROeOStaPQJhc1SSwl9Zd79W2bA35B1o4oopg5d9HsMc12nOe-t