）</li>	<li>热力学（Thermodynamics）</li>	<li>内部燃烧引擎（Internal Combustion Engines）*(6)</li></ul><p>机械工程系建议攻读MS（Non thesis option）项目的学生从以下领域中选择6-8门课程（建议选择全部核心课程，再从相关课程中选择部分其它课程）：</p><ul>	<li>能源技术（Energy Technology）</li>	<li>固体力学（Solid Mechanics）</li>	<li>设计与制造（Design and Manufacturing）</li>	<li>流体力学与热科学（Fluid Mechanics and Thermal Sciences）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_2CwBdbNxwkIIIIIIUEnr-2UyfBHMhcAM5v1M1Lx4rZxxlAIR-nrxlvCZo7VZoKSsTO8lk4Nj3X5N0cklP_4i" target="_blank">Full-time Faculty</a></li>	<li>实验室列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6bHwSnOKhYEVPBvAffI4TfrkUKzJrumVgmt1hN6FqoxDfta9kPpfazWKKVt0MpOdIfueZ9zhQO0QnkRHfVMu7WJykd_A9wQtLQzP3eX" target="_blank">Our Research and Teaching Labs</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vB2wjNSrTdkimcPr0dQeNYKFE0ftliT4bdMfspM4Tcv2B8-3VvvxcfEJ4cENtN1Ms2gkmH8OL7Xdn9mIfEoABbw1TOeCgRjltRfvMuBAByMFu9gchog9OhxXx" target="_blank">Cost of Attendance</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZCwBdbNF6MHHHHHHXmvLF-1yu2QYGYwB_bphRqykhqq8HPmDh75AHX_Bhty8HtaIGP7jHVcAHtkA0hRoKteYGw" target="_blank">Graduate Admissions</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(3) <a href="https://www.grad.stonybrook.edu/ProspectiveStudents/faq.shtml#scores" target="_blank">Admission FAQs-test scores</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHWw_8kIm0OKKKKKKQDpAb5PTjHsc-o5csFrDho3V-U33Fqj3RaHwCHMhSm-FCcpwkmLUfzvriHiqjr5qcTCbStN_iNxP" target="_blank">Degree Requirements for the Ph.D. Degree in Mechanical Engineering</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvIkJVBToAui9Xs9YRVvjNvCf-mKgsWH3b_C2gDsUBgzmGNOt058nUVm9eGkADRKRupOAsK_sWIzI7F73e0Wz4yBy_4OxbL0Fp" target="_blank">Degree Requirements for the M.S. Degree in Mechanical Engineering</a> Stony Brook University</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWS9